snippet: Millions have watched a parody of “Les Misérables” put out by the South Korean Air Force and inspired by the “Gangnam Style” video.
abstract: Parody of movie musical Les Miserables featuring members of South Korean Air Force becomes viral hit after just five days on YouTube.

byline.contributor: Shreeya Sinha contributed reporting from New York.

lead_paragraph: Millions have watched a parody of “Les Misérables” put out by the South Korean Air Force and inspired by the “Gangnam Style” video.

headline.seo: ‘Les Militaribles,’ South Korean Video Spoof, Goes Viral
headline.main: ‘Les Miz’ Meets ‘Gangnam Style,’ and YouTube Cheers
